name: strFileCfg
description: location of the configuration file

name: help
description: to print help information

name: show
description: to show configuration value

name: dryRun
description: to check input without running encoding

name: idxFra
description: index of the current frame

name: idxLcuX
description: index of the current LCU in the X (horizontal) direction

name: idxLcuY
description: index of the current LCU in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: trueSizLcuX
description: true size of the current LCU in the X (horizontal) direction

name: trueSizLcuY
description: true size of the current LCU in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: enmTyp
description: slice type of the current frame (<value> 0: intra; 1 inter)

name: datQpFra
description: QP value of the current frame

name: datQpLcu
description: QP value of the current LCU

name: strFileYuv
description: location of the YUV file

name: strPrefixDump
description: dump prefix

name: strPrefixLoad
description: load prefix

name: enmLvlEnc
description: level of encoding (<value> 0: hardware 1: software)

name: enmLvlLog
description: level of the output log (<value> 0: no log; 1: enable basic log; 2: enable frame-level log; 3: enable LCU-level log; 4: enable PU/TU/CU-level log)

name: flgDmpCsv
description: enable flag for the dump of csv-format log

name: flgDmpYuvRec
description: enable flag for the dump of reconstructed YUV

name: flgDmpDbg
description: enable flag for the dump of debug information

name: flgDistortion
description: enable flag for (the calculation of) distortion (<index> 0/1: PSNR/MS-SSIM)

name: flgSizCuIntra
description: enable flags for the corresponding CU sizes in intra frames (<index> 0/1/2/3: size 08/16/32/64)

name: flgSizCuInter
description: enable flags for the corresponding CU sizes in inter frames (<index> 0/1/2/3: size 08/16/32/64)

name: flgPrtCuIntra
description: enable flags for the corresponding PU partitions in intra frames (<index> 0/1: 2Nx2N/1Nx1N partition)

name: flgPrtCuInter
description: enable flags for the corresponding PU partitions in inter frames (<index> 0/1/2/3: 2Nx2N/2Nx1N/1Nx2N/1Nx1N partition)

name: numFra
description: number of the frames to be processed

name: idxFraBgn
description: index of the first frame to be processed

name: numChn
description: number of channels (Y/U/V)

name: sizFraX
description: size of the frame in the X (horizontal) direction

name: sizFraY
description: size of the frame in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: sizSwX
description: size of the search window (excluding LCU) in the X (horizontal) direction

name: sizSwY
description: size of the search window (excluding LCU) in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: sizLcu
description: size of LCU

name: enmStd
description: standard (0: H264; 1: H265; 2: NSTD; 3: H266)

name: enmModRun
description: run mode (0: encode; 1: decode)

name: datLvl
description: level (valid under H264 standard)

name: datFps
description: frames per second

name: datQpSeq
description: QP value of the current sequence

name: datPrdIntra
description: period of intra frames (-1: I(P)(P)(P)...; 0: (I)(I)(I)...; 1: (IP)(IP)(IP)...; 2: (IPP)(IPP)(IPP)...)

name: ltrFlg
description: enable flag for LTR (long term reference)

name: ltrEnmMod
description: mode of LTR (0: always referring to I frames; 1: referring to the nearest long term P frames or I frames)

name: ltrDatPrd
description: period of LTR frames (0: (L)(L)(L)...; 1: (LS)(LS)(LS); 2: (LSS)(LSS)(LSS)...)

name: gopSiz
description: size of gop

name: gopEnmTyp
description: frame types in one gop

name: gopDatPoc
description: picture order counter in one gop

name: gopDatQpDlt
description: delta QP in one gop

name: gopFlgRefNeg
description: enable flags for negative references in one gop

name: gopFlgRefPos
description: enable flags for positive references in one gop

name: gopNumRefPos
description: number of positive references in one gop

name: gopDatPocRefDltNeg
description: delta POC of negative references in one gop

name: gopDatPocRefDltPos
description: delta POC of positive references in one gop

name: roiIdxLcuBgnX
description: index of ROI's begin LCU in the X (horizontal) direction

name: roiIdxLcuBgnY
description: index of ROI's begin LCU in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: roiIdxLcuEndX
description: index of ROI's begin LCU in the X (horizontal) direction

name: roiIdxLcuEndY
description: index of ROI's begin LCU in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: roiFlgTyp
description: enable flag for block types of ROI

name: roiEnmTyp
description: block types of ROI (<value> 0: intra; 1: inter; 2: skip)

name: roiFlgQp
description: enable flag for QP of ROI

name: roiDatQp
description: QP value of ROI

name: r_cFlg
description: enable flags (<index> 0: ratio based frame-level RC; 1/2: smooth based LCU-level intra/inter RC; 3/4: SADR based LCU-level intra/inter RC; 5/6: SATD based LCU-level intra/inter RC; 7: SAMV based LCU-level inter RC)

name: r_cDatBps
description: target bit rate of averaged frames (unit: kbps)

name: r_cDatBpsIntra
description: target bit rate of intra frames (unit: kbps)

name: r_cDatBpsInter
description: target bit rate of inter frames (unit: kbps)

name: r_cDatQpMinIntra
description: minimum QP allowed in intra frames

name: r_cDatQpMinInter
description: minimum QP allowed in inter frames

name: r_cDatQpMaxIntra
description: maximum QP allowed in intra frames

name: r_cDatQpMaxInter
description: maximum QP allowed in inter frames

name: r_cDatThrRatiIntra
description: threshold of RATI based frame-level intra RC (unit: 6*log2)

name: r_cDatDltRatiIntra
description: delta QP  of RATI based frame-level intra RC

name: r_cDatThrRatiInter
description: threshold of RATI based frame-level inter RC (unit: 6*log2)

name: r_cDatDltRatiInter
description: delta QP  of RATI based frame-level inter RC

name: r_cDatSclSmthIntra
description: smooth scaler of SMTH based LCU-level intra RC (could be taken as the reciprocal of LCU number to be smoothed)

name: r_cDatSclSmthInter
description: smooth scaler of SMTH based LCU-level inter RC (could be taken as the reciprocal of LCU number to be smoothed)

name: r_cDatThrSmthIntra
description: (minimum) threshold of SMTH based LCU-level intra RC

name: r_cDatThrSmthInter
description: (minimum) threshold of SMTH based LCU-level inter RC

name: r_cDatDltSmthIntra
description: (maximum) delta QP of SMTH based LCU-level intra RC

name: r_cDatDltSmthInter
description: (maximum) delta QP of SMTH based LCU-level inter RC

name: r_cDatPrmSmthIntra
description: parameter of SMTH based LCU-level intra RC

name: r_cDatPrmSmthInter
description: parameter of SMTH based LCU-level inter RC

name: r_cDatThrSadrIntra
description: threshold of SADR based LCU-level intra RC

name: r_cDatDltSadrIntra
description: delta QP  of SADR based LCU-level intra RC

name: r_cDatThrSadrInter
description: threshold of SADR based LCU-level inter RC

name: r_cDatDltSadrInter
description: delta QP  of SADR based LCU-level inter RC

name: r_cDatThrSatdIntra
description: threshold of SATD based LCU-level intra RC

name: r_cDatDltSatdIntra
description: delta QP  of SATD based LCU-level intra RC

name: r_cDatThrSatdInter
description: threshold of SATD based LCU-level inter RC

name: r_cDatDltSatdInter
description: delta QP  of SATD based LCU-level inter RC

name: r_cDatThrSamvInter
description: threshold of SAMV based LCU-level inter RC

name: r_cDatDltSamvInter
description: delta QP  of SAMV based LCU-level inter RC

name: iipEnmStg
description: decision stage of IIP (<value> 0: disable IIP; 1: do IIP decision in IME stage; 2: do rough IIP decision in IME stage and do final IIP decision in RDO stage; 3. do IIP decision in RDO stage; 4. do IIP decision in CFG stage (fix ratio and fix position))

name: iipEnmScl
description: scaler type (<value> 0: on D+lambdaR 1: on lambdaR)

name: iipDatRatio
description: the reciprocal of the ratio of iip blocks

name: iipDatSclOnMv
description: scale to bias intra blocks (<index> 0/1/2/3/4: scaler under MV 0~7/8~15/16~23/24~31/31~inf 1/4 pixel)

name: mrgEnmLvl
description: merge level (<value> 0: none; 1: simple; 2: extra)

name: mrgNum
description: maximum number of candidates

name: skpFlg
description: enable flags for skip (<index> 0: luma; 1:chroma)

name: skpEnmScl
description: scaler type (<value> 0: on D+lambdaR 1: on lambdaR)

name: skpDatSclOnChn
description: scaler to bias skip blocks (<index> 0/1: scaler for luma/chroma)

name: skpDatSclOnMv
description: scale to bias skip blocks (<index> 0/1/2/3/4: scaler under MV 0~7/8~15/16~23/24~31/31~inf 1/4 pixel)

name: rmdFlgRun
description: enable flag

name: rmdEnmModLoad
description: load mode (<value> 0: load from pipe; 2. load from file; 3. load random data)

name: rmdNumGrp
description: number of the intra-mode groups to be tested for each PU

name: rmdSizGrp
description: size   of the intra-mode groups to be tested for each PU

name: rmdDatMod
description: data   of the intra-mode groups to be tested for each PU

name: rmdEnmCst
description: cost type (<value> 0: SAD; 1: HAD)

name: imeFlgRun
description: enable flag

name: imeEnmModLoad
description: load mode (<value> 0: load from pipe; 1. load from file; 2. load random data)

name: imeNumPtn
description: number of the patterns to be tested for each LCU

name: imeEnmCtr
description: center types to be tested for each pattern (<index> N: the Nth pattern) (<value> 0: use the center specified by imePosCtrX/Y; 1: use the best result of LCU; 2: use the best result of 0th QLCU; 3: use the best result of 1st QLCU; 4: use the best result of 2nd QLCU; 5: use the best result of 3rd QLCU)

name: imePosCtrX
description: center positions in the X (horizontal) direction to be tested for each pattern (<index> N: the Nth pattern)

name: imePosCtrY
description: center positions in the Y (vertical)   direction to be tested for each pattern (<index> N: the Nth pattern)

name: imeSizPtnX
description: sizes in the X (horizontal) direction to be tested for each pattern (<index> N: the Nth pattern)

name: imeSizPtnY
description: sizes in the Y (vertical)   direction to be tested for each pattern (<index> N: the Nth pattern)

name: imeEnmSlp
description: slopes to be tested for each pattern (<index> N: the Nth pattern) (<value> 0: 0.5; 1: 1.0; 2: 2.0; 3: infinite)

name: imeFlgD_s
description: enable flags for downsampling to be tested for each pattern (<index> N: the Nth pattern)

name: imeNumBitCut
description: number of bits cut

name: imeDatSclMvd
description: scaler to bias mvd cost

name: fmeFlgRun
description: enable flag

name: fmeEnmModLoad
description: load mode (<value> 0: load from pipe; 1. load from file; 2. load random data)

name: fmeNumCtr
description: number of the search centers to be tested for each PU (valid and only valid for inter blocks)

name: fmeEnmCtr
description: type of the search centers to be tested for each PU (valid and only valid for inter blocks) (<index> N: the Nth search center) (<value> 0: best results of FME; 1: MvpA; 2: MvpB; 3: 0-0)

name: fmeNumItp
description: number of the interpolation for each search center (valid and only valid for inter blocks) (<index> N: the Nth search center)

name: fmeEnmItp
description: type of the interpolations to be tested for each search center (valid and only valid for inter blocks) (<index> N-M: the Nth search center Mth interpolation) (<value> 0: none; 1: quarter; 2: half)

name: fmeFlgNei
description: enable flag for neighbour testing for each PU (valid and only valid for inter blocks) (<index> 0: 0-0; 1: 0--1; 2: 0-1; 3: -1-0; 4: 1-0; 5:-1--1; 6:-1-1; 7: 1--1; 8: 1-1)

name: fmeEnmCst
description: cost type (<value> 0: SAD; 1: HAD; 2: SAD and MVD; 3: HAD and MVD)

name: fmeDatSclMvd
description: scaler to bias mvd cost

name: rdoFlgRun
description: enable flag

name: rdoEnmModLoad
description: load mode (<value> 0: load from pipe; 1. load from file; 2. load random data)

name: rdoFlgCh
description: enable flag for chroma channel testing (<index> 0: intra frames; 1: inter frames)

name: rdoEnmSrcMod
description: source type of the intra modes to be tested for each PU (valid and only valid for intra blocks) (<value> 0: modes from RMD; all the valid modes)

name: rdoNumMod
description: number of the intra modes to be tested for each PU (valid and only valid for intra blocks)

name: rdoFlgTstLu01
description: enable flag for forcely testing luma mode 0 and 1 (valid and only valid for intra blocks)

name: rdoFlgSetCh36
description: enable flag for forcely setting chroma modes to 36 (valid and only valid for intra blocks)

name: rdoNumCtr
description: number of the search centers to be tested for each PU (valid and only valid for inter blocks)

name: rdoEnmCtr
description: type of the search centers to be tested for each PU (valid and only valid for inter blocks) (<index> N: the Nth search center) (<value> 0: best results of FME; 1: MvpA; 2: MvpB; 3: 0-0)

name: rdoNumItp
description: number of the interpolation for each search center (valid and only valid for inter blocks) (<index> N: the Nth search center)

name: rdoEnmItp
description: type of the interpolations to be tested for each search center (valid and only valid for inter blocks) (<index> N-M: the Nth search center Mth interpolation) (<value> 0: none; 1: quarter; 2: half)

name: rdoFlgNei
description: enable flag for neighbour testing for each PU (valid and only valid for inter blocks) (<index> 0: 0-0; 1: 0--1; 2: 0-1; 3: -1-0; 4: 1-0; 5:-1--1; 6:-1-1; 7: 1--1; 8: 1-1)

name: rdoEnmCst
description: cost type (<index> 0: intra; 1: inter) (<value> 0: SAD; 1: HAD; 2: SAD and MVD; 3: HAD and MVD; 4: SSE and FIT; 5: SSE and SEC)

name: rdoFlgRdoq
description: enable flags for rdoq (<index> 0/1/2-0/1/2/3: co/cg/lst of intra luma/intra chroma/inter luma/inter chroma)

name: rdoFlgSkpTsf
description: enable flags for transform skip (<index> 0/1: intra luma/chroma; 2/3 inter luma/chroma)

name: rdoDatSclLmd
description: scaler to bias lambda (<index> 0/1: intra luma/chroma; 2/3 inter luma/chroma)

name: rdoDatFitICu
description: parameter of intra rate cost's CU part (<index> 0: partition 1Nx1N; 1: partition 2Nx2N)

name: rdoDatFitIPu
description: parameter of intra rate cost's PU part (<index> 0/1/2/3: luma channel with mpm index -1/0/1/2; 4/5: chroma channel with mpm index -1/0)

name: rdoDatFitITuS
description: parameter of intra rate cost's TU part (slope) (<index> 0/1/2/3: luma channel with TU 04/08/16/32; 4/6: chroma channel with TU 04/08/16)

name: rdoDatFitITuI
description: parameter of intra rate cost's TU part (intercept) (<index> 0/1/2/3: luma channel with TU 04/08/16/32; 4/6: chroma channel with TU 04/08/16)

name: rdoDatFitPCu
description: parameter of inter rate cost's CU part (<index> 0: partition 2Nx2N)

name: rdoDatFitPPu
description: parameter of inter rate cost's PU part (<index> 0: merge flag with value 0; 1: merge flag with value 1; 2/3: mvp index with value A/B; 4/5: merge index with value 0/1; 6/7 slope and intercept of mvd data)

name: rdoDatFitPTuS
description: parameter of inter rate cost's TU part (slope) (<index> 0: luma channel with TU 08; 1: luma channel with TU 16; 2: luma channel with TU 32; 4: chroma channel with TU 04; 5: chroma channel with TU 08; 6: chroma channel with TU 16)

name: rdoDatFitPTuI
description: parameter of inter rate cost's TU part (intercept) (<index> 0: luma channel with TU 08; 1: luma channel with TU 16; 2: luma channel with TU 32; 4: chroma channel with TU 04; 5: chroma channel with TU 08; 6: chroma channel with TU 16)

name: recFlgRun
description: enable flag

name: recEnmModLoad
description: load mode (<value> 0: load from pipe; 1. load from file; 2. load random data)

name: ilfFlgRun
description: enable flag

name: ilfEnmModLoad
description: load mode (<value> 0: load from pipe; 1. load from file; 2. load random data)

name: ilfFlgDbf
description: enable flag for feature DBF

name: ilfFlgSao
description: enable flag for feature SAO (<index> 0: luma 1: chroma)

name: ilfDatOffBtDiv2
description: parameter BetaOffsetDiv2 for feature DBF

name: ilfDatOffTcDiv2
description: parameter   TcOffsetDiv2 for feature DBF

name: ilfDatSclLmd
description: scaler to bias lambda (<index> 0/1: intra luma/chroma; 2/3 inter luma/chroma)

name: e_cFlgRun
description: enable flag

name: e_cFlgSbh
description: enable flag for sign bit hidden

name: e_cEnmModLoad
description: load mode (<value> 0: load from pipe; 1. load from file; 2. load random data)

name: e_dFlgRun
description: enable flag

name: e_dEnmModLoad
description: load mode (<value> 0: load from pipe; 1. load from file; 2. load random data)

name: itfFlgRfc
description: enable flag for feature RFC

name: dmpEnmLvlTop
description: dump level of TOP related test vector

name: dmpEnmLvlRmd
description: dump level of RMD related test vector

name: dmpEnmLvlIme
description: dump level of IME related test vector

name: dmpEnmLvlFme
description: dump level of FME related test vector

name: dmpEnmLvlRdo
description: dump level of RDO related test vector

name: dmpEnmLvlIlf
description: dump level of ILF related test vector

name: dmpEnmLvlE_c
description: dump level of E_C related test vector

name: dmpEnmLvlE_d
description: dump level of E_D related test vector

name: dmpEnmLvlItf
description: dump level of ITF related test vector

name: numLst
description: number of reference lists of one frame

name: numLcuX
description: number of LCUs in the X (horizontal) direction of one frame

name: numLcuY
description: number of LCUs in the Y (vertical)   direction of one frame

name: numCu
description: number of CUs in the X/Y (horizontal/vertical) direction of one LCU

name: numPu
description: number of PUs in the X/Y (horizontal/vertical) direction of one LCU

name: num4x4
description: number of 4x4 blocks in the X/Y (horizontal/vertical) direction of one LCU

name: numLaC
description: number of channels (luma/chroma)

name: numMod
description: (maximum) number of modes

name: numMpm
description: (maximum) number of MPMs

name: trueSizFraX
description: true size of the frame in the X (horizontal) direction

name: trueSizFraY
description: true size of the frame in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: sizSchX
description: size of the search window (including LCU) in the X (horizontal) direction

name: sizSchY
description: size of the search window (including LCU) in the Y (horizontal) direction

name: trueSizSwX
description: true size of the search window (excluding LCU) in the X (horizontal) direction

name: trueSizSwY
description: true size of the search window (excluding LCU) in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: sizTuMax
description: maximum size of TU in the X/Y (horizontal/vertical) direction

name: sizRecExt
description: extended size of rec buffer in the X/Y (horizontal/vertical) direction

name: sizRefExt
description: extended size of ref buffer in the X/Y (horizontal/vertical) direction

name: sizIipExtX
description: extended size of iip buffer in the X (horizontal) direction

name: sizIipExtY
description: extended size of iip buffer in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: sizModExtX
description: extended size of mod buffer in the X (horizontal) direction

name: sizModExtY
description: extended size of mod buffer in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: sizFmvExtX
description: extended size of fmv buffer in the X (horizontal) direction

name: sizFmvExtY
description: extended size of fmv buffer in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: sizCbfExtX
description: extended size of cbf buffer in the X (horizontal) direction

name: sizCbfExtY
description: extended size of cbf buffer in the Y (vertical)   direction

name: datDepCu
description: depth of CUs

name: datModHor
description: intra mode for horizontal direction

name: datModVer
description: intra mode for vertical   direction

name: gopNumReorderPics
description: number of reorder pictures

name: gopDatPocCur
description: current POC

name: gopDatPocCurAbs
description: current POC (absolute)

name: gopDatPocRefDltNegCur
description: current delta POC of negative references

name: gopDatPocRefDltPosCur
description: current delta POC of positive references

name: gopDatPocRefNegCur
description: current POC of negative references

name: gopDatPocRefPosCur
description: current POC of positive references

name: gopDatPocRefNegCurAbs
description: current POC of negative references (absolute)

name: gopDatPocRefPosCurAbs
description: current POC of positive references (absolute)

name: gopIdxRefLast
description: last reference used in one gop

name: rdoFlgRdoqAny
description: if any rdoq is enabled

name: rdoFlgSkpTsfAny
description: if any transform skip is enabled
